{it:barlook_options}
    set the look of the bars.  The most important of these options is
    {cmd:color(}{it:colorstyle}{cmd:)}, which specifies the color of the
    bars; see {manhelpi colorstyle G-4} for a list of color choices.  See
    {manhelpi barlook_options G-3} for information on the other
    {it:barlook_options}.
